Package net.emuman.spigotutils.gui

Class FullDynamicSidebar

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.scheduler.BukkitRunnable
      • net.emuman.spigotutils.gui.PartialDynamicSidebar
        • net.emuman.spigotutils.gui.FullDynamicSidebar
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    public class FullDynamicSidebar
extends PartialDynamicSidebar
    A sidebar that can be dynamically set and updated. The difference between this class and the PartialDynamicSidebar is that all 48 characters in any given line can be updated. However, this comes with a slight performance/execution cost, and all 15 lines must be present, so when possible, use PartialDynamicSidebar.
